2. Update /app/api/agent/route.ts to accept thinkingMode
   and forward thinking SSE events
3. Add thinkingMode to Zustand store + setThinkingMode action
4. Create /components/chat/ThinkingBlock.tsx
5. Update ChatMessage interface to include thinking fields
6. Update ChatMessage component to render ThinkingBlock
7. Update chat sendMessage handler to process thinking SSE events
8. Add thinking mode selector to AgentControlPanel
9. Add pulse/bounce CSS animations to global styles
10. Update SKILL.md with <planning> block requirement
11. Test: send "make a scene about black holes" with thinking=adaptive
    → verify thinking block appears in chat, streams, then collapses
12. Test: send "make the title bigger" with thinking=adaptive
    → verify thinking is skipped (adaptive mode)
13. Test: switch to thinking=off → verify no thinking block appears
14. Test: switch to thinking=deep → verify longer reasoning block

